# Rock Paper Scissors

A simple game where you play rock paper scissors against the computer.
The computer picks randomly and the program tells you who won.

## How to run
python main.py

## How to run tests
python -m pytest test_main.py

## What I learned
- How to use random.choice
- How to use while loop to keep game running
- How to check multiple conditions using or
- How to handle invalid user input